 <p>Sarabeth, Lvl 44 Mith Marr Magician of Freeport<BR>
Andih [Holfstetz], 10 Peacekeeper of Quellious<BR>
Moduna Nossum, The Nameless<BR>
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=balthemal>Balthemal</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Master Summoner</span><br>  Posts: 225<br> <font color=#333333>(2/25/02 9:16:56 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm37.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Where to hunt at level 4 in EC?</span><hr size=1> EC is not the best place to go...try EQ atlas for more info. <p><b><font size="1"><a target="new" href="http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Id=60066">Balthemal </a><br>54 Mage<br>Fennin Ro</font></b></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=magetlow>magetlow</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 21<br> <font color=#333333>(11/6/02 12:23:00 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm37.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Where to hunt at level 4 in EC?</span><hr size=1> 1 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=pazilla>Pazilla</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 22<br> <font color=#333333>(12/21/02 1:18:32 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm37.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Where to hunt at level 4 in EC?</span><hr size=1> If you want to hunt in EC, fight spiderlings, fire beetles, orc pawns, black wolves and decaying skeletons.  The last three will not generate xp after you hit 5.<br>
<br>
Northern Ro, I think is better at these levels.  Desert spiderlings, fire beetles, decaying skeletons, coyotes and armadilloes.  In fact, you can get most of your newbie armor quest gear in Northern Ro except Black Bear Paws, Shadow Wolf Tibia and Orc Prayer Beads. <p>Panzilla Gatecrasher,45 Beastlord<br>
