<br>
Use the soulbinder in EFP to rebind, wait until you can handle everything in EFP near guards.  When that is all under control,  move to NRO, and either hunt near the zone line, or near the guards next to the inns.  <br>
<br>
EC seems to have 3-4 times as many people as NRo on my server, which tends to be fairly empty except for Derv camps. <br>
